    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SAMAGO is an endless 2D precision platformer with a 24-hour twist! Every level is available for just 24 hours, giving you a limited time to compete against other players before it resets. Can you push your limits, go the farthest, and claim the top spot on the leaderboards today?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >24-Hours Cycle</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For 24 hours every player has the same level layout, as you play you can see other players' attempts from all over the world! After 24-Hours a new level is formed and scores are reset.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258710/extras/baf49525370e5766890c11c0aeb011a3.poster.avif?t=1760529940\" width=800 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258710/extras/baf49525370e5766890c11c0aeb011a3.webm?t=1760529940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258710/extras/baf49525370e5766890c11c0aeb011a3.mp4?t=1760529940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Compete With Others</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter other players on the map as &quot;ghost frogs.&quot; But be careful—the ghosts can snatch your coins if you're not quick enough!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258710/extras/33bbb06893495f65bae045e8961cec10.avif?t=1760529940\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258710/extras_big/33bbb06893495f65bae045e8961cec10.avif?t=1760529940 width=1560 height=720 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Practice, Practice, And Practice </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want to have a more relaxed time? Play in PRACTICE MODE, after each run level layout is changed. Enjoy this more casual approach to SAMAGO and when you have honed your skills feel free to climb up the leaderboards in main mode! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258710/extras/c04823199bc50cd6ea16d607bc351f11.poster.avif?t=1760529940\" width=800 height=454 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258710/extras/c04823199bc50cd6ea16d607bc351f11.webm?t=1760529940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258710/extras/c04823199bc50cd6ea16d607bc351f11.mp4?t=1760529940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Make Your Frog Your Own</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your Frog with different types, costumes, and trails that can be seen by other players!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258710/extras/edc0282745f679cbaf3addd29a43a0b7.poster.avif?t=1760529940\" width=800 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258710/extras/edc0282745f679cbaf3addd29a43a0b7.webm?t=1760529940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258710/extras/edc0282745f679cbaf3addd29a43a0b7.mp4?t=1760529940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Decorate Your Frog Pond</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Personalize your very own frog pond by decorating it with collectible furniture and accessories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect Rewards</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn daily rewards by ranking among the top five on the leaderboards. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New Level And Leaderboard Every Day</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >See Other Player's Attempts As &quot;Ghost Frogs&quot;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate Your House</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize Your Frog</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless platformer level</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online Leaderboards</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >...And More!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258710/extras/85bbf3aae00a0d77f33a58950a6be74c.poster.avif?t=1760529940\" width=616 height=532 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258710/extras/85bbf3aae00a0d77f33a58950a6be74c.webm?t=1760529940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258710/extras/85bbf3aae00a0d77f33a58950a6be74c.mp4?t=1760529940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
